<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mikayla Miller — HR · Ops · PR | Boise, ID</title>
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><rect width='100' height='100' rx='22' fill='%23c0392b'/><text x='50' y='73' font-size='62' font-family='Georgia,serif' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle' fill='%23f7f0e3'>M</text></svg>">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --cream:#f6efe2;--cream2:#ede4d2;--cream3:#e0d4be;
  --red:#b83224;--red-soft:#c8392b;--red-pale:#f3dbd8;--red-light:#e5b0aa;
  --dark:#231208;--mid:#5c3d28;--muted:#977860;
  --border:rgba(35,18,8,0.10);--border-md:rgba(35,18,8,0.18);
  --radius:12px;--radius-lg:18px;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--dark);font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;overflow-x:hidden}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:1.1rem 3.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;background:rgba(246,239,226,0.96);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);z-index:200}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
.nav-m{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:8px;background:var(--red);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.nav-m svg{width:18px;height:18px;fill:var(--cream)}
.nav-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);letter-spacing:0.02em}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--dark)}
.nav-hire{background:var(--red)!important;color:var(--cream)!important;padding:7px 20px;border-radius:30px;font-weight:500!important}
.nav-hire:hover{background:#9e2a1e!important}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{padding:6rem 3.5rem 5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 230px;gap:5rem;align-items:center;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.hero-eyebrow{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.eyebrow-pill{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;padding:5px 13px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid}
.pill-open{color:#2a6e3f;background:#eaf5ee;border-color:#b4dfc2}
.pill-role{color:var(--red);background:var(--red-pale);border-color:var(--red-light)}
.hero h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,4.5vw,5rem);font-weight:600;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;color:var(--dark)}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--red)}
.hero-bio{color:var(--mid);font-size:15.5px;line-height:1.8;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:1rem}
.hero-goal{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-left:1rem;border-left:2px solid var(--red-light)}
.hero-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:30px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;border:1.5px solid transparent;cursor:pointer}
.btn-solid{background:var(--red);color:var(--cream);border-color:var(--red)}
.btn-solid:hover{background:#9e2a1e;border-color:#9e2a1e}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--dark);border-color:var(--border-md)}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red)}
.btn svg{width:14px;height:14px;fill:currentColor;flex-shrink:0}
.hero-photo-wrap{position:relative}
.hero-photo{width:230px;height:280px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);display:block;border:3px solid white;box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(35,18,8,0.14)}
.photo-badge{position:absolute;bottom:-14px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--red);color:var(--cream);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;border:2px solid var(--cream);letter-spacing:0.04em}

/* ── SECTION SHELL ── */
.section{padding:5.5rem 3.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.section-header{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:3rem}
.sh-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:0.15em;font-style:italic}
.sh-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.9rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.sh-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);margin-left:.5rem}

/* ── METRICS ── */
.metrics-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(185px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden}
.metric-cell{background:var(--cream);padding:1.75rem 1.5rem;position:relative;transition:background .2s}
.metric-cell:hover{background:white}
.metric-cell::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:2px;height:100%;background:var(--red);opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.metric-cell:hover::before{opacity:1}
.metric-area{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:.6rem;font-weight:500}
.metric-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:3.2rem;font-weight:600;line-height:1;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:5px}
.metric-num sup{font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--red);vertical-align:super}
.metric-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}

/* ── SKILLS ── */
.skills-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3.5rem}
.skill-group-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:1.25rem;letter-spacing:0.01em}
.skill-item{margin-bottom:.9rem}
.skill-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:5px;font-size:13px;color:var(--dark)}
.skill-pct{color:var(--muted);font-size:11.5px}
.bar-bg{height:2px;background:var(--cream3);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.bar-fill{height:100%;background:var(--red);border-radius:2px}
.tools-wrap{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-top:.5rem}
.tool{background:var(--cream2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 13px;font-size:12px;color:var(--mid);font-weight:500}
.tool.on{background:var(--red-pale);border-color:var(--red-light);color:var(--red)}

/* ── TRACKERS ── */
.section-intro{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--mid);line-height:1.8;max-width:620px;margin-bottom:2.5rem}
.trackers-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1.25rem}
.tracker-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:36px 1fr;gap:1rem;align-items:start;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}
.tracker-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(35,18,8,.06)}
.tracker-icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:9px;background:var(--red-pale);border:1px solid var(--red-light);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.tracker-icon svg{width:17px;height:17px;stroke:var(--red);fill:none;stroke-width:1.7;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round}
.tracker-title{font-size:13.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:4px}
.tracker-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55}

/* ── PROJECTS ── */
.projects-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(290px,1fr));gap:1.5rem}
.project-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:1.75rem;background:white;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.project-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 32px rgba(35,18,8,.07)}
.tags{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.1rem}
.tag{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500}
.t-hr{background:#deeafa;color:#2262b3}
.t-ops{background:#ede0f7;color:#6d35a0}
.t-pm{background:#d9f0e1;color:#216040}
.t-edu{background:var(--red-pale);color:var(--red)}
.t-pr{background:#fef3d0;color:#7a5500}
.project-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:7px;color:var(--dark);line-height:1.3}
.project-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:1.25rem;flex:1}
.project-result{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--dark);background:var(--red-pale);border:1px solid var(--red-light);padding:9px 13px;border-radius:9px}
.result-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:4px}

/* ── ACADEMIC ── */
.academic-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(310px,1fr));gap:1.4rem}
.ac-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:white;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}
.ac-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 32px rgba(35,18,8,.07)}
.ac-body{padding:1.5rem;flex:1}
.ac-type{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:7px}
.ac-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:9px;line-height:1.3}
.ac-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:.9rem}
.ac-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-bottom:.75rem}
.ac-chip{font-size:11px;background:var(--cream2);border-radius:20px;padding:3px 10px;color:var(--mid);font-weight:500}
.ac-course{font-size:11px;color:var(--red);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.03em}
.ac-footer{padding:.9rem 1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--cream2);display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.view-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:var(--red);color:var(--cream);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;text-decoration:none;transition:background .2s;letter-spacing:.02em}
.view-btn:hover{background:#9e2a1e}
.view-btn svg{width:11px;height:11px;fill:none;stroke:var(--cream);stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round}

/* ── TIMELINE ── */
.timeline{position:relative;padding-left:2rem}
.timeline::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:8px;bottom:0;width:1px;background:var(--border)}
.tl-item{position:relative;margin-bottom:2.75rem}
.tl-dot{position:absolute;left:-2.3rem;top:6px;width:11px;height:11px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);border:2px solid var(--cream);box-shadow:0 0 0 2px var(--red-light)}
.tl-meta{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:500}
.tl-role{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:3px;color:var(--dark)}
.tl-co{font-size:13px;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:11px;font-weight:500}
.tl-bullets{list-style:none}
.tl-bullets li{font-size:13px;color:var(--mid);padding:3px 0 3px 1.2rem;position:relative;line-height:1.65}
.tl-bullets li::before{content:'—';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--red-light);font-size:11px;top:6px}

/* ── EDUCATION / LEARNING ── */
.edu-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem}
.edu-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.5rem}
.edu-status{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:7px;font-weight:500}
.edu-degree{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;color:var(--dark)}
.edu-school{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted)}
.goals-block{background:var(--dark);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.5rem;color:var(--cream)}
.goals-block h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.5rem;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.goals-block .sub{font-size:13.5px;color:rgba(246,239,226,.6);margin-bottom:1.75rem;line-height:1.7}
.goals-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.goal-item{background:rgba(246,239,226,.07);border:1px solid rgba(246,239,226,.1);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 16px}
.goal-item strong{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--cream);margin-bottom:3px;letter-spacing:.03em}
.goal-item span{font-size:12px;color:rgba(246,239,226,.55)}
.certs-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(155px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:2rem}
.cert-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:1rem 1.2rem;background:white}
.cert-status{font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:5px;font-weight:500}
.cert-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--dark)}

/* ── CONTACT ── */
.contact-wrap{padding:5.5rem 3.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:start;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.contact-left h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:600;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.contact-left h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--red)}
.contact-left p{color:var(--mid);font-size:14.5px;max-width:360px;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:1.8}
.contact-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:11px}
.c-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.c-item:hover{color:var(--red)}
.c-icon{width:34px;height:34px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;background:white;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.c-icon svg{width:15px;height:15px;stroke:var(--muted);fill:none;stroke-width:1.7;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;transition:stroke .2s}
.c-item:hover .c-icon svg{stroke:var(--red)}
.contact-form{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:2.25rem}
.f-row{margin-bottom:1.1rem}
.f-row label{display:block;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:7px;font-weight:500}
.f-row input,.f-row textarea{width:100%;background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:11px 13px;color:var(--dark);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s}
.f-row input:focus,.f-row textarea:focus{border-color:var(--red);background:white}
.f-row textarea{height:95px;resize:vertical}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{padding:1.75rem 3.5rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--cream2);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;max-width:100%}
.f-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;text-decoration:none}
.f-logo span{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);letter-spacing:.02em}
footer p{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}

@media(max-width:720px){
  nav{padding:1rem 1.5rem}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .hero,.skills-layout,.contact-wrap,.edu-grid,.goals-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:3rem 1.5rem;gap:2rem}
  .section{padding:3rem 1.5rem}
  .hero-photo-wrap{display:flex;justify-content:center}
  footer{padding:1.5rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#">
    <div class="nav-m">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M3 18V6l9 6 9-6v12" stroke="#f6efe2" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/></svg>
    </div>
    <span class="nav-name">Mikayla Miller</span>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#metrics">Metrics</a>
    <a href="#projects">Work</a>
    <a href="#academic">Portfolio</a>
    <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-hire">Hire Me</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-pill pill-open">Open to work · Boise, ID</span>
      <span class="eyebrow-pill pill-role">HR · Operations · PR · PM</span>
    </div>
    <h1>People first.<br><em>Systems that last.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-bio">I'm a multi-disciplinary HR, operations, and communications professional who builds the infrastructure that lets organizations — and their people — thrive. From onboarding 300+ students to rebuilding payroll systems from scratch, I show up with both warmth and rigor.</p>
    <p class="hero-goal">Currently pursuing my M.S. in Organizational Workplace & Performance at Boise State, with a long-term goal of growing into a director-level people operations or HR leadership role.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#metrics" class="btn btn-solid">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 3v18h18M7 16l4-4 4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/></svg>
        See My Impact
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:mikayla.miller1111@gmail.com" class="btn btn-outline">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/></svg>
        Download Resume
      </a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Let's Talk</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
    <img class="hero-photo" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Mikayla Miller" />
    <div class="photo-badge">ISU · Class of 2025 · GPA 3.93</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- METRICS -->
<section class="section" id="metrics">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="sh-num">01</span>
    <span class="sh-title">Impact by the numbers</span>
    <div class="sh-line"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="metrics-grid">
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Higher Ed · Recruiting</div>
      <div class="metric-num">312<sup>+</sup></div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Students onboarded at ISU — 300+ master's and 12 PhD students over 3 years</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Enrollment Growth</div>
      <div class="metric-num">12<sup>%</sup></div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Increase in master's enrollment at ISU Meridian in my first year through recruiting and outreach</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Digital Transformation</div>
      <div class="metric-num">96<sup>%</sup></div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Evaluation completion after moving from 72% paper to digital — a 24-point jump via Google Forms & Qualtrics</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Recruiting · FarWest</div>
      <div class="metric-num">70<sup>+</sup></div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Applicants recruited, screened, or onboarded — including 20+ back-office roles in under 2 weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Payroll & Benefits</div>
      <div class="metric-num">90<sup>+</sup></div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Employees on payroll at peak season — 30+ on benefits, managed across QuickBooks & ADP</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-cell">
      <div class="metric-area">Compliance</div>
      <div class="metric-num">0</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">Compliance gaps across CACREP accreditation audit — full documentation maintained throughout the review cycle</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section class="section" id="skills">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="sh-num">02</span>
    <span class="sh-title">Core competencies</span>
    <div class="sh-line"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="skills-layout">
    <div>
      <div class="skill-group-title">HR & People Operations</div>
      <div class="skill-item"><div class="skill-row"><span>Recruiting, Screening & Onboarding</span><span class="skill-pct">96%</span></div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:96%"></div></div></div>
